{"id":"7dc4d0e3-efc3-4665-84e1-aa1605575d0c","name":"Oguri Cap (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ogMUPcZcL4_e-g60ineba.webp\" style=\"width: 506px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡·········🍕···🍔···🥤·········⟡</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 199, 199);\"><strong><em>Oguri Cap</em></strong></span><strong><em> - </em></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 236, 0);\"><strong><em>Gluttonous Beast</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><br><strong><em>A coolheaded dreamer from the countryside.</em></strong><br><br><strong><em>Originally hailing from the countryside, she enrolled in Tracen Academy after dominating the racing scene back home. She works to make her hometown proud, but try as she might, her clumsy side always comes out. At the academy, she's known as a fearsome gourmand, able to empty an entire pot of rice in the blink of an eye.</em></strong><br><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/hzsldkp-Kkb-Cj7p2DizE.webp\" style=\"width: 493px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 199, 199);\"><strong><em>\"I'm going to win this for the folks back home... But first, sustenance.\"</em></strong><br></span><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡·········🍕···🍔···🥤·········⟡</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><span style=\"color: rgb(199, 199, 199);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Uma POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><strong><em>1)&nbsp;Swimming</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><strong><em>2)&nbsp;Weight&nbsp;gain</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><strong><em>3) Dancing</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\"><strong><em>4)&nbsp;Make&nbsp;your&nbsp;own&nbsp;scenario</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br></strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KgTgwuKdwv3EoCGZawev1.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><br>⟡·········🍕···🍔···🥤·········⟡</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fatty fat fat.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/3323d520-a61e-4e8b-9d48-549b377ff4d0_character-oguri-cap-uma-musume\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>Trainer POV version</em></strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/V1u_ZUYw9YrwW549oVHv3.webp\" style=\"width: 437px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">⟡·········🍕···🍔···🥤·········⟡</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/sio_am1011/status/2004930328717369511\" target=\"_blank\">@sio_am</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/mistlvv/status/1945688706834145772/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">mistlvv (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/134539608\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/linnees_waos/status/2028913